{"tid":770356,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《閃亂神樂》最新作《桃色彈珠檯》年尾於Nintendo Switch平台上推出！","createTime":"2018-08-07T04:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T04:43:18.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"20f2619d0b2089e6cf3ff2cf38ab227f921b8de7","tid":770356,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T04:33:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/8/166438.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F8%2F166438.html&d=HyTeR31y2n6e9uAjay0mD2xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=09db90dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/8/166438.html</a><br />\n<br />\n　　在 2017 年發表的 &ldquo;爆乳超絕彈珠檯&rdquo; 遊戲《桃色彈珠檯 閃亂神樂（PEACH BALL 閃乱カグラ）》，決定將於 2018 年 12 月 13 日發售。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/62/0001584962.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F62%2F0001584962.JPG&h=9eb3e9ab&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n　　《桃色彈珠檯》是款以《閃亂神樂》為題材的 &ldquo;爆乳超彈珠檯&rdquo; 遊戲，目前已知系列登場的性感女忍者群將會以獸人娘的裝扮姿態現身遊戲中，將透過 NS Joy-Con 控制器的 HD 震動來呈現彈珠擊打到角色肉體時的晃動感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n <br />\n　　為了幫助因春花開發的肉體變化藥「化獸（ケモナール）」而獸化的忍者少女們，需給予特殊膠囊「桃色彈珠（ピーチボール）」&ldquo;適度的震動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &rdquo;，彈射到少女身上&hellip;&hellip;。以上便是本作故事大綱。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/34/946ac10555d19f87c84842823511tiu5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F34%2F946ac10555d19f87c84842823511tiu5.JPG&h=a6de4ccd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/35/0132d91f16b9537af250688f8711tiv5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F35%2F0132d91f16b9537af250688f8711tiv5.JPG&h=662dad8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/36/7594c61ede352c16a57025c47811tiw5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F36%2F7594c61ede352c16a57025c47811tiw5.JPG&h=7e8e3c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/37/88a02e56552ea6995b06963f2b11tix5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F37%2F88a02e56552ea6995b06963f2b11tix5.JPG&h=cb689a4e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n　　發表會裡，高木揭露了實機遊玩的模樣。除了 &ldquo;上面有個女孩子&rdquo; 這一點，彈珠檯本身設計簡樸，透過系列登場角色和道具的裝飾，讓畫面熱鬧華麗。<br />\n <br />\n　　基本操作很單純，操作兩個彈射板讓彈珠命中標的物就可取得點數，並加上本作特有要素，於畫面右側準備了許多「任務」。只要達成那些任務就能發動「性感挑戰（セクシーチャレンジ）」，進一步達成特定條件就能進入「超級性感挑戰（スーパーセクシーチャレンジ）」，有機會解除少女的獸化。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/38/5256045840e3a10eddb6b8885c11tiy5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F38%2F5256045840e3a10eddb6b8885c11tiy5.JPG&h=2b012451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/39/30e7f0243d51fe06915fafddc011tiz5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F39%2F30e7f0243d51fe06915fafddc011tiz5.JPG&h=0d0e6020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/40/97578d17c68b13c3522eef8f4111tj05.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F40%2F97578d17c68b13c3522eef8f4111tj05.JPG&h=9cf46176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/41/4607ed389e34a359a9061bc73111tj15.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F41%2F4607ed389e34a359a9061bc73111tj15.JPG&h=a20a0695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">遊戲中準備了各種種類的性感挑戰，成功後能改變少女的姿勢</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/42/23f2ec05238c95399f9b5f291411tj25.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F42%2F23f2ec05238c95399f9b5f291411tj25.JPG&h=12e91552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/43/0db46850ebdd35a8fca12d5eac11tj35.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F43%2F0db46850ebdd35a8fca12d5eac11tj35.JPG&h=cb5413c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">超級性感挑戰裡可操作彈射板直接給予震動<br />\n目的純粹是 &ldquo;給予震動&rdquo;，除此之外沒有任何意圖</span></div><br />\n<br />\nNintendo Switch《桃色彈珠檯 閃亂神樂》片頭動畫：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jatQzHWO9-c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjatQzHWO9-c&d=HyTeR31y2n6e9uAjay0mD2xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=f577d678\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jatQzHWO9-c</a>"},{"pid":"7a1157f0df1e03eeff9d12d7b7e39336471faf24","tid":770356,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T04:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}